---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="搜尋"
  description="搜尋網站上所有英文新聞文章"
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pt-10 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">
      搜尋 · Search
    </h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mb-8">
      在所有文章標題、內容、單字解釋裡搜尋。可以輸入英文或中文。
    </p>

    {/*
      Pagefind UI gets mounted into this div. The search index files (built
      by `npx pagefind --site dist` in bin/build_for_deploy.sh) live at
      /pagefind/* in the deployed site. Both UI script and CSS load from
      there too, so this page only needs the empty container plus a tiny
      bootstrap script.
    */}
    <div id="search" class="pagefind-mount"></div>

    {/* Show a friendly hint while pagefind hasn't loaded yet (e.g. dev mode). */}
    <noscript>
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 mt-4">
        搜尋需要 JavaScript 才能運作，請在瀏覽器開啟 JavaScript。
      </p>
    </noscript>

    <p
      id="search-fallback"
      class="hidden mt-6 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400"
    >
      搜尋索引載入中⋯⋯如果一直顯示這個訊息，可能你正在本機 dev 模式（搜尋只在 build 後可用），或網路連線有問題。
    </p>
  </article>

  {/*
    Pagefind UI assets live in /pagefind/ at the deployed site root. We use
    inline tags (instead of <link>/<script> in <head>) so this only loads on
    /search and doesn't slow down other pages.
  */}
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/pagefind/pagefind-ui.css" />
  <script is:inline src="/pagefind/pagefind-ui.js"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      // Pagefind loads asynchronously. If after 3 seconds we still don't
      // have a PagefindUI constructor, show the fallback hint.
      var fallbackTimer = setTimeout(function () {
        var el = document.getElementById("search-fallback");
        if (el) el.classList.remove("hidden");
      }, 3000);

      function init() {
        if (typeof PagefindUI === "undefined") {
          // Try again on next tick — script may not have parsed yet.
          setTimeout(init, 100);
          return;
        }
        clearTimeout(fallbackTimer);
        new PagefindUI({
          element: "#search",
          showSubResults: true,
          showImages: false,
          translations: {
            placeholder: "搜尋⋯⋯（試試 OpenAI、climate、台積電）",
            clear_search: "清除",
            load_more: "載入更多",
            search_label: "搜尋本站",
            filters_label: "篩選",
            zero_results: "找不到符合「[SEARCH_TERM]」的結果",
            many_results: "共 [COUNT] 篇結果符合「[SEARCH_TERM]」",
            one_result: "找到 1 篇結果符合「[SEARCH_TERM]」",
            alt_search:
              "找不到「[SEARCH_TERM]」。改顯示「[DIFFERENT_TERM]」的結果：",
            search_suggestion: "找不到「[SEARCH_TERM]」。試試這些：",
            searching: "搜尋「[SEARCH_TERM]」中⋯⋯",
          },
        });
      }
      init();
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
